title: Chad Lawson Discography 2011-2013 (4 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
CHAD LAWSON DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 2011 - A Solo Piano Christmas
 * 2011 - The Piano
 * 2012 - Songs Of Prayer- Solo Piano Music For Prayer
 * 2013 - The Space Between

Chad Lawson is a jazz pianist/keyboardist living in New York City. Chad Lawson is currently an endorser for Steinway & Sons Pianos.

Blessings,
TorrentTracts - September 2013
